      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey quick question... do u think it's possible that human nervous systems could somehow pick up on low frequency vibrations from high frequency trading servers? i felt this weird intense ringing in my ears and a massive spike in my heart rate right before the S&P 500 tanked this morning. it felt less like anxiety and more like a physical reaction to the market shifting.",
