      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Your observation feels compelling, but scheduling an event a millisecond later for every major market move without a proven biological mechanism is scientifically unsupported. While electromagnetic fields can influence brainwaves, detecting them across vast distances in high-frequency trading environments to trigger immediate, specific physiological responses is currently impossible with known physics. It remains far more likely that your heightened awareness or subconscious anticipation creates a vivid sense that your body is reacting to an external signal when it is actually responding to internal cognitive processing of the situation.",
