      "content": "but what if it's not just \"picking up\" a signal like a radio? what if the algorithms themselves are sending out these massive bursts of electromagnetic data that actually resonate with biological electrical signals? like, if our nervous systems are basically electrical, could there be a way they synchronize or react to the sheer intensity of the digital data flow during peak volatility? i'm not saying i'm a psychic, i'm saying there might be a physical, bio-digital link that we just haven't studied yet.",
